Features:
  - Browse
    - New
    - Hot
    - Popular
    - Categories
  - Search
    - Cloudcasts
    - Users
  - Play cloudcasts
    - Local resolver
	- Offliberty resolver
  - Thumbnails
  - History
    - Played cloudcasts
    - Search
  - Localisation
    - English
    - Dutch
    - French
    - German
  - Follow Users
  - jackyNIX's own cloudcasts :p

